# Runtime and compilation

Read-only graph from store/callbacks; **never** assign into `graph`, `graph.nodes`, or `graph.connections`. Use **`src/data-model`** types.

Parameter updates flow like the app (`onParameterChange`, etc.); compiler receives graphs that already passed **`validateGraph`** (see serialization rule).

After edits: grep/scan for mutations in `src/runtime/**` and `src/shaders/**` (compilation); run `npm run build` + relevant tests.

**Refs:** `.cursor/rules/data-model/graph-updates.mdc`, core-architecture _OVERVIEW (§01, §03A–§04).
